{"tid":1344701,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠日本偶遇小學生　事後捐出200萬贊助旅程","createTime":"2019-07-22T00:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T09:31:12.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4b42f6ae415aabf62197cfedc5fe97c660fd66","tid":1344701,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190719/s00010/591ff2a2fd4a8580c11d6a6b0368def6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190719%2Fs00010%2F591ff2a2fd4a8580c11d6a6b0368def6.jpg&h=c7de0bb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190719/s00010/59212af60d7d380d458870136d45e119.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190719%2Fs00010%2F59212af60d7d380d458870136d45e119.jpg&h=d7ae8e89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190719/s00010/593493d497082c224e818599b3271aed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190719%2Fs00010%2F593493d497082c224e818599b3271aed.jpg&h=a48e567c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190719/s00010/59e1be29d7508720b31efec60432c0d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190719%2Fs00010%2F59e1be29d7508720b31efec60432c0d1.jpg&h=c024d061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：新浪財經微博<br />\n<br />\n《新浪財經》在其微博上載多張本港首富李嘉誠，在日本北海道機場現身的照片，指有內地幾位老師帶著40多名小學生到日本進行舞蹈比賽，意外地在該機場偶遇李嘉誠，其後更獲這位首富捐出200萬元(人民幣‧下同)，贊助他們這次行程。<br />\n<br />\n從照片所見，久未在香港露面的誠哥精神奕奕，表現得相當興奮，與一眾小朋友合照及揮手。據新浪的微博指，誠哥在偶遇這班小孩之後，便吩咐自己的秘書聯繫帶隊老師，要從李嘉誠慈善基金捐出100萬元，用於贊助這45位小學生。<br />\n<br />\n本報經與基金會了解後，發言人確認捐款屬實。今次捐款對象是上海小白鴿舞蹈團，資助範圍包括90萬元補助45名學員參加於2019年7月18日在日本北海道「國際青少年舞蹈大會」之相關旅費；10萬元補助舞蹈團因參加是次海外賽事的開支；100萬元讓舞蹈團於未來推行老年人學習舞蹈的公益項目。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在該微博下留言指：「我小孩子就在裡面，是李嘉誠慈善基金給舞蹈機搆一百萬，然後再負擔小孩子們去北海道參加比賽的所有費用約80萬，再給每個小朋友送一份禮物(小朋友去商場自己選，他埋單)」。<br />\n<br />\n儘管近年李嘉誠被內地傳媒連番報道其撤資的負面消息，惟誠哥仍對內地人和事始終不離不棄。今次偶遇的經過，被同行的其中一位老師在其微博上公開，有網民笑問「誰能告訴我李嘉誠先生下一站的機場名稱和時間」、又指誠哥非常親民及「接地氣」，紛紛祝他老人家身體健健康康。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1563521802590&amp;issue=20190719\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1563521802590%26issue%3D20190719&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=927eaab7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1563521802590&amp;issue=20190719</a>"},{"pid":"ce04b4f92a237195cc04ec57255374df8c7c55ac","tid":1344701,"uid":259700,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:19:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49dfa59fcbe986f3b0089476905dd85331d6d4be","tid":1344701,"uid":62842,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"示範完美從大陸撤資既同時唔會比大陸人屌到仆街"},{"pid":"2dbe2ec5bb676380d45808cdb85f3f3d03641c1e","tid":1344701,"uid":174530,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:47:00.000Z","msg":"即係香港大眾夾手夾腳捐"},{"pid":"fb538a24e86db623c53fe65b5b71593a95064ba7","tid":1344701,"uid":30468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"49dfa59fcbe986f3b0089476905dd85331d6d4be","tid":1344701,"uid":62842,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"示範完美從大陸撤資既同時唔會比大陸人屌到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:34:24.000Z","msg":"完美PR<br />\n不愧為嘉誠哥"},{"pid":"12f14ba918d98775d1107d5c5ebe70eeeed5b2f4","tid":1344701,"uid":15660,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"ce04b4f92a237195cc04ec57255374df8c7c55ac","tid":1344701,"uid":259700,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:19:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T21:43:56.000Z","msg":"咁都叫廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317ac72cebaad930aa5d2ff749a985c14bd99371","tid":1344701,"uid":22694,"like":21,"dislike":0,"s